**Explanation of the regex**:

  - `(`: Start of capturing group#1
    - `\\d*\\.`: Digit(s) followed by `.`
    - `0*`: Any number of zeros
    - `[1-9]{4}`: Non-zero four digits 
  - `)`: End of capturing group#1
  - `\d*` : Any digit any number of times


